commit.message:
feat(sprint-11): D-05 parametric EQ, D-06 compressor, U-09 drag reorder

- D-05: 4-band parametric EQ per input strip (low shelf, 2x peak, high shelf)
  Audio EQ Cookbook biquad filters; EqParams serialised into StripParams/scenes;
  #[serde(default)] for backward-compat with old scenes; EqProcessor runtime state
  POST /api/v1/channels/input/:id/eq; EQ modal in web UI with per-band controls
- D-06: Peak compressor/limiter per output bus; attack/release envelope follower;
  CompressorParams serialised into BusParams; #[serde(default)] for old scenes;
  POST /api/v1/channels/output/:id/compressor; COMP button + modal in web UI
- U-09: Channel drag-and-drop reorder; input_order/output_order in AppState;
  POST /api/v1/channels/input/reorder + /output/reorder (permutation validated);
  GET /api/v1/state now includes input_order + output_order; matrix renders
  in server-provided order; HTML5 drag events on matrix rows
- 50 tests passing (6 new for eq/compressor)

